Editor's note: Livestream courtesy DStv 403 and you can watch it on DStv Now. JOHANNESBURG - The Nelson Mandela Centenary celebrations are well under way. This time, his 27 years as a political prisoner are being remembered in a new collection called The Prison Letters of Nelson Mandela. The documents were assembled from a collection from the Nelson Mandela Foundation and the SA National Archives. Many of these letters have never been made public before. eNCA